---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CtaSection from '../components/CtaSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | HeatherAI" description="The story behind HeatherAI — 20+ years of nutrition coaching expertise, now available to everyone.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 pt-28 pb-20">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-[1.1] max-w-[800px] tracking-tight">
      Built on <em class="not-italic text-accent">20 years</em> of real coaching.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/50 max-w-[560px] leading-relaxed mt-6">
      HeatherAI isn't another AI chatbot with a nutrition prompt. It's the product of two decades
      of hands-on coaching, distilled into technology that actually changes behavior.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- The Journey -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-white/[0.06]">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-12 text-center">The Journey</h2>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-white/55 text-base leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-white block mb-1">It started with one-on-one coaching.</strong>
          Heather Bauer, RDN, built her practice in New York City working with clients who needed
          more than a meal plan. They needed someone who understood their habits, their triggers,
          and the real-world pressures that derail even the most motivated people.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Then came the methodology.</strong>
          Over 20+ years, Heather developed coaching patterns that worked — consistently. A
          scaffold-then-release approach that starts intensive and lightens as habits form.
          Personalized strategies based on who you are, not a generic template.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong class="text-white block mb-1">5,000+ clients later, the patterns were proven.</strong>
          More than a million coaching messages. Thousands of clients who transformed their
          relationship with food. Real data showing what works — and what doesn't.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Then came the question: what if this could scale?</strong>
          The biggest limitation of great coaching is access. Heather can only work with so many
          people. HeatherAI was built to bring those proven coaching patterns to everyone —
          without compromising what makes them work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Methodology -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-white/[0.06]">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-12 text-center">The Methodology</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="p-8 bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Behavior over information</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">
            Most people already know what to eat. The challenge is doing it consistently.
            HeatherAI coaches behavior change, not nutrition facts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Scaffold, then release</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">
            Intensive coaching early on, with a gradual shift toward independence.
            The goal is self-sufficiency, not dependency.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Personalized archetypes</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">
            Not everyone needs the same approach. HeatherAI recognizes different client
            patterns and adapts its coaching accordingly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-bg-surface border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Real conversations</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/45 leading-relaxed">
            Coaching happens in the moment — at the restaurant, at the grocery store,
            when motivation dips. Not in a scheduled appointment once a month.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bridge to AI -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-white/[0.06] text-center">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">The Bridge to AI</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Every response HeatherAI gives is rooted in patterns that have worked for thousands of real clients.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-white/40 leading-relaxed">
        It's not a replacement for human expertise — it's a way to make that expertise accessible
        to everyone, every day, in the moments that matter most.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <CtaSection
    headline={"Experience coaching that works."}
    subline="Start with free meal logging. No credit card required."
    ctaText="Try HeatherAI"
  />
</BaseLayout>
